item.title: SoftLayer_Network_Storage_Hub_Swift
item.description: SoftLayer_Network_Storage_Hub_Swift Datatype Description seeAlso SoftLayer_Network_Storage Local accountId The internal identifier of the SoftLayer customer account that a Storage account belongs to. Type: integer capacityGb A Storage account's capacity, measured in gigabytes. Type: integer createDate The date a network storage volume was created. Type: dateTime guestId The unique identification number of the guest associated with a Storage volume.
